---
title: Chermoula Chicken & Veggie Risoni with Lemon Yoghurt
description: This dish is inspired by the lively and vibrant night markets of Marrakech – it’s packed with loads of colour, aroma and zest, made only more authentic by the perfectly charred chermoula-spiced chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-spiced-chicken-09b3d0da.jpg
